<div class="jumbotron">
	<div class="container">
		<h1>Internet Video Game Library</h1>
		<p>Welcome to Internet Video Game Library! Here you can keep track of your backlog and get information about all your games.</p>
		<p><%= link_to new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg"  do%>Sign up now &raquo;<% end %></p>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="container">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-4">
			<h2>All game releases in one place!</h2>
			<p>Japanese, European, North American or Brazillian. All releases organized and linked so that you can easily navigate between one another.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-4">
			<h2>Custom lists</h2>
			<p>We already prepared five lists for you: Wishlist, Backlog, Playing, Played and Finished. But if you want to keep track of the games you achieved 100%, you can create another list.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-4">
			<h2>Community built</h2>
			<p>Everyone can sign up to edit and insert new games. This way, the database is always up-to-date. Ask to be a game master and you'll have all this super powers!</p>
		</div>
		<div class="clearfix"></div>
		<div class="col-md-4">
			<h2>Current status</h2>
			<p>We currently have <%= @work_count %> unique games, <%= @editions_count %> editions and <%= @expansions_count %> Expansions/DLC in our database!</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row">
		<h2>Recently added games</h2>
	</div>

	<div class="row" id='recently_added_games'>
		<% @games.each_with_index do |game, i| %>
			<%- if i > 0 && ( (i % 6 == 0) || (i % 4 == 0) || (i % 2 == 0) )%>
				<div class="clearfix<%- if (i % 6 == 0) %> visible-md visible-lg<% end -%><%- if (i % 4 == 0) %> visible-sm<% end -%><%- if (i % 2 == 0) %> visible-xs<% end-%>"></div>
			<% end -%>
			<%= render partial: "shared/games_index_view_object", locals: {game: game, user_shelves: @user_shelves} %>
		<% end %>
	</div>

	<hr>
</div>
